{"tid":945034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"衛報：摩連奴帥位安全，他已經在準備下場比賽","createTime":"2018-12-17T14:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:55:42.000Z","uid":124292,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4c135590ed6651562dddcadb539c0cf9ff7bf081","tid":945034,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"根據《衛報》曼聯隨隊記者Jamie Jackson報道，摩連奴儘管帶隊輸給利物浦，但他的帥位在近期仍然是安全的。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴正在面對越來越大的壓力，因為曼聯本賽季表現不佳，目前只排在聯賽第六，但《衛報》瞭解到摩連奴將繼續留在主帥位置上。<br />\n<br />\n17輪比賽過後，曼聯落後榜首的利物浦19分，落後第四名車路士11分，摩連奴的球隊淨勝球為0，這是曼聯自1990年以來的最差開局。<br />\n<br />\n由於聯賽盃被淘汰，摩連奴有一周的時間來準備周六和卡迪夫城的比賽。"},{"pid":"266ff947b1a8c7a4d02f0fad0ee5b1ac6d9a9afb","tid":945034,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"Free fall <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19fed55fcd3a4d49de595943685ac0517955911","tid":945034,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"永續喇"},{"pid":"f3e289087aaefc39d4c5d75c7442bccc07c3dedf","tid":945034,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"摩佬是無辜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93038794a0c39238a4d6e1dbb8222fbfc437c0d","tid":945034,"uid":196078,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"**[下場比賽],摩佬親自落場踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sure win"},{"pid":"ce8787d9476d8437628fbedd1a206bef7073b77b","tid":945034,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098fb987238688b6e77b115c300c6fe5c393e580","tid":945034,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f93038794a0c39238a4d6e1dbb8222fbfc437c0d","